Package frc.robot.helpers

Class ControllerWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • frc.robot.helpers.ControllerWrapper
  • public class ControllerWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    A wrapper for WPILib's XboxController class. Importantly, it adds the ability to retrieve a WPILib Button. Utilized by instiating a new ControllerWrapper rather than an XboxController. Any XboxController-specific submethods can be retrieved by driver.getController().getRawAxis(1) or the like. Buttons/D-pad directions are referenced using driver.bA or driver.dNE, for example.
